3","text":"Thou therefore endure hardness, as a good soldier of Jesus Christ.","year":66},{"id":"recnaAAYVieXjgA7Y","ref":"2Tim.2.4","text":"No man that warreth entangleth himself with the affairs of this life; that he may please him who hath chosen him to be a soldier.","year":66},{"id":"recqGHKcTRX6wf4zm","ref":"2Tim.2.5","text":"And if a man also strive for masteries, yet is he not crowned, except he strive lawfully.","year":66},{"id":"recREcOJXgD264S8v","ref":"2Tim.2.6","text":"The husbandman that laboureth must be first partaker of the fruits.","year":66},{"id":"recKCRBY6tWD3MkZw","ref":"2Tim.2.7","text":"Consider what I say; and the Lord give thee understanding in all things.","year":66},{"id":"rec9ispYbuxJUBqrA","ref":"2Tim.2.8","text":"Remember that Jesus Christ of the seed of David was raised from the dead according to my gospel:","year":66}]}
